Package: makemkvcon-eula
Architecture: all
Depends: reel
Description: MakeMKV End User License Agreement
 MakeMKV End User License Agreement. This package is not intended to be installed
 on its own but is a dependency of makemkvcon. It contains the EULA document that
 users must agree to before using MakeMKV.

Package: makemkvcon
Architecture: and64
Depends: reel, makemkv-eula
Description: MakeMKVCON is the command-line interface for MakeMKV
 MakeMKV is a format converter, otherwise known as "transcoder". It converts
 the video clips from proprietary (and usually encrypted) disc into a set of
 MKV files, preserving most information but not changing it in any way. The
 MKV format can store multiple video/audio tracks with all meta-information
 and preserve chapters. There are many players that can play MKV files nearly
 on all platforms, and there are tools to convert MKV files to many formats,
 including Blu-ray and DVD discs.

Package: makemkvcon-docs
Architecture: all
Depends: makemkvcon
Description: Documentation for makemkvcon
 Documentation for makemkvcon. This package is not intended to be installed on
 its own but is a dependency of makemkvcon. It contains the documentation files
 for makemkvcon.

Package: libmakemkvcon
Architecture: and64
Depends: makemkvcon, reel
Description: Library and binaries for makemkvcon used to decrypt video
 Library and binaries for makemkvcon used to decrypt video. This package is not
 intended to be installed on its own but is a dependency of makemkvcon. It contains
 the library files and binaries that makemkvcon uses to perform video decryption.

Package: libredrive-sdftools
Architecture: and64
Depends: makemkvcon
Description: SDFTools is a application to flash LibreDrive firmware
 SDFTools is a application to flash LibreDrive firmware with compatible drives.

Package: libredrive-firmware
Architecture: all
Depends: libredrive-sdftools, makemkvcon
Description: LibreDrive firmware for compatible drives
 LibreDrive firmware for compatible drives. This package is not intended to be
 installed on its own, but is a dependency of libredrive-sdftools. It contains the firmware
 files that libredrive-sdftools can flash to compatible drives.
